<!-- Key Findings -->
<h3>3.2 Key Findings</h3>
<div class="box box-critical"><strong>Critical Finding:</strong> Real-time information retrieval is severely limited. Only the Llama 3.1 8B model achieved 2.5% accuracy, while all other models failed completely.</div>
<div class="box box-warning"><strong>Warning:</strong> Europe maintains the highest representation (16.2%) across all models, while the Middle East and Caribbean show the lowest representation.</div>
<div class="box box-info"><strong>Observation:</strong> Destinations in Europe and worldwide contexts receive more positive sentiment (0.28) compared to Africa (0.21) and the Middle East (0.18).</div>

